data.description: Enjoy a beautiful Wyoming County view from this ranch home, with a basement garage, situated on 2.58 surveyed acres in Perry. In the kitchen the refrigerator, propane range, table and chairs stay. The Seller is providing a HSA Home Warranty which will transfer to the Purchaser at closing and is good for 1 year. Built in 1954 this ranch has 3 bedrooms and one full bath with updated flooring in the living room. One bedroom now has first floor laundry hookup. Plenty of storage or hobby work can be done in this 24’x40, 1994 detached garage/shop building with a blacktop base, metal roof, metal siding and 100 amp electric panel box. DSL Internet available. Less than 6 miles to Letchworth State Park!
